Params: {1: '1', 2: '"Sand Fox"', 3: "That's the last one! Phew, these bats are such a pain to deal with.", 4: '1'}
{3: '"Sand Fox" holsters his gun, watching as the distant Hetero-Creature plummets to the ground.'}
{3: "After escorting 【kuroname】's group into the Babel Tower, the Support Force begins their return journey toward New Oakley."}
{1: '1', 2: '"Sand Fox"', 3: 'Lizard, take inventory of our combat supplies.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: '"Lizard"', 3: "You don't have to tell me twice. I'm already on it.", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: '"High Wall"', 3: "We lost contact with 【kuroname】's group after they entered the tower. I wonder if everything's okay.", 4: '3'}
{2: '"Sand Fox"', 3: "They've got it. Not our job to wor—w-what the—****!!!", 4: '1'}
{2: '"Lizard"', 3: 'Why are you stuttering all of a sudden?!', 4: '2'}
{2: '"Sand Fox"', 3: 'Those bats are back!! A ****ing SWARM of them!!!', 4: '1'}
{2: '"Sand Fox"', 3: 'High Wall, floor that ****ing pedal NOW!!', 4: '1'}

{3: 'In the distance, a swarm of black specks emerges from the direction of the Babel Tower, coalescing into a seething dark cloud that devours the sky. The horde of Hetero-Creatures surges toward the convoy, an unstoppable tide.'}
{3: 'But everyone present knows the truth—against such numbers, survival is nearly impossible.'}
{3: 'Yet as the shadow looms closer and bullets tear through the swarm, the Support Force members begin to notice something off.'}
{3: 'The swarm of Hetero-Creatures sweeps past the convoy, flying straight toward the horizon.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bridget', 3: "Quick! Leave anything that's not important! Elders, children, and other non-combatants, get in the cars first!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bridget', 3: 'Where are the other Task Force members?!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Mayor Max watches the townspeople evacuating in panic, his brow deeply furrowed.', 6: '3'}
{2: 'Max', 3: "I hope... there's still time for everyone.", 4: '1'}
